# PATCH: 0001-plugin-manager-hook
# WHY: Tinh nang plugin (ADR-0001) can 1 diem hook DUY NHAT trong core de start Plugin
#      Manager + mount API dong /api/plugins/ TREN subrouter da qua middleware authentication.
#      Logic that o quickwin.dev/pluginmanager. Rebase: tim lai cho tao authenticatedAPI
#      (PathPrefix "api" + Use(...authentication)) roi goi registerQuickwinPlugins ngay sau.
# WHAT: file MOI api/quickwin_plugins.go (keo: env QUICKWIN_PLUGINS_DIR, Scan+Start,
#      GET /api/plugins list + mount /api/plugins/ dong, map user->Caller); router.go +1 dong;
#      go.mod +require/replace quickwin.dev/{pluginmanager,proto,sdk}. go.sum generated (go mod tidy).
# SPEC: docs/L2-specs/core-patches/0001-plugin-manager-hook.md
# BASELINE: v2.18.16
#
